'''罗马尼亚人团结联盟'''<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-12/07/c_1126832987.htm|title = 罗马尼亚议会选举初步结果显示社民党得票领先|website = 新华网|date = 2020-12-07|language = zh|accessdate = 2020-12-11|archive-date = 2020-12-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201211111544/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-12/07/c_1126832987.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>（{{lang-ro|Alianța pentru Unirea Românilor}}，缩写为AUR）是[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]的一个[[右翼|右翼]][[民族主义|民族主义]]政党，成立于2019年12月1日，在[[2020年羅馬尼亞議會選舉|2020年议会选举]]中在参众两院均取得超过9%的选票，超过5%的门槛成功进入[[罗马尼亚议会|罗马尼亚议会]]。

==历史==
该党于2019年12月1日[[国家统一日_(罗马尼亚)|国家统一日]]成立于[[阿尔巴尤利亚|阿尔巴尤利亚]]，象征着罗马尼亚统一的城市。领导人{{link-ro|乔治·西蒙|George Simion}}称该党打算参加{{le|2020年罗马尼亚地方选举|2020 Romanian local elections}}和[[2020年罗马尼亚国会选举|立法选举]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dcnews.ro/george-simion-a-lansat-alianta-pentru-unirea-romanilor-aur-pentru-romani_714717.html|title=George Simion a lansat Alianța pentru Unirea Românilor. Este AUR|first=Cristina|last=Scutaru|newspaper=DCNews|date=2019-12-01|accessdate=2020-12-07|language=ro|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202064959/https://www.dcnews.ro/george-simion-a-lansat-alianta-pentru-unirea-romanilor-aur-pentru-romani_714717.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年6月26日，该党谴责罗马尼亚当局对[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]和[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]境内[[罗马尼亚人|罗马尼亚人]]的[[少数人权利|少数民族权利]]漠不关心，并宣布一旦进入[[罗马尼亚议会|议会]]，它将全力支持这些权利<ref>{{cite news|url=https://rgnpress.ro/2020/06/26/aur-condamnam-ferm-dezinteresul-autoritatilor-romane-fata-de-comunitatile-romanesti-din-serbia-si-ucraina/|title=AUR: Condamnăm ferm dezinteresul autorităților române față de comunitățile românești din Serbia și Ucraina|newspaper=Romanian Global News|date=2020-06-26|accessdate=2020-12-07|language=ro|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728083430/https://rgnpress.ro/2020/06/26/aur-condamnam-ferm-dezinteresul-autoritatilor-romane-fata-de-comunitatile-romanesti-din-serbia-si-ucraina/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两天后，该党在[[苏联|苏联]][[苏联占领比萨拉比亚和北布科维纳|占领]][[比萨拉比亚|比萨拉比亚]]、[[布科维纳|北布科维纳]]和[[赫尔扎地区|赫尔扎地区]]80周年纪念日谴责了侵略行为，宣称“我们有义务夺回我们的国家”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://infoprut.ro/64237-indemnul-aur-la-80-de-ani-de-la-rapirea-basarabiei-bucovinei-de-nord-si-a-tinutului-herta-este-datoria-noastra-sa-ne-recuperam-statul.html|title=Îndemnul AUR la 80 de ani de la răpirea Basarabiei, Bucovinei de Nord și a Ținutului Herța: "Este datoria noastră să ne recuperăm statul"|first=Ana|last=Marchitan|newspaper=InfoPrut|date=2020-06-28|accessdate=2020-12-07|language=ro|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728084932/https://infoprut.ro/64237-indemnul-aur-la-80-de-ani-de-la-rapirea-basarabiei-bucovinei-de-nord-si-a-tinutului-herta-este-datoria-noastra-sa-ne-recuperam-statul.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

截至7月11日，该党在[[欧洲|欧洲]]和[[北美|北美]]为{{le|罗马尼亚侨民|Romanian diaspora}}设立了22个分支机构<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.romaniatv.net/diaspora-mesaj-catre-bucuresti-lasati-ne-sa-calatorim-liber_529413.html|title=Diaspora, mesaj către București: Lășați-ne să călătorim liber!|newspaper=RomaniaTV.Net|date=2020-07-11|accessdate=2020-12-07|language=ro|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728083425/https://www.romaniatv.net/diaspora-mesaj-catre-bucuresti-lasati-ne-sa-calatorim-liber_529413.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一个分支机构在[[英国|英国]]的[[伍尔弗汉普顿|伍尔弗汉普顿]]建立<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mediafax.ro/politic/primul-partid-din-romania-care-propune-incheierea-unui-contract-intre-candidat-si-alegator-18674579|title=Primul partid din România care propune încheierea unui contract între candidat şi alegător|first=Elena|last=Crangasu|newspaper=Mediafax|location=Bucharest|date=2019-12-20|accessdate=2020-12-07|language=ro|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220183244/https://www.mediafax.ro/politic/primul-partid-din-romania-care-propune-incheierea-unui-contract-intre-candidat-si-alegator-18674579|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该党是罗马尼亚唯一一个表示支持[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]的政党。<ref name="europa_liberă">{{Cite web |date=2020-12-06 |title=AUR obține peste 8%. George Simion: Nu vom face alianțe. Claudiu Târziu: Suntem apărătorii Bisericii |url=https://romania.europalibera.org/a/draft-aur/30986837.html |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208085340/https://romania.europalibera.org/a/draft-aur/30986837.html |archive-date=2020-12-08 |access-date=2020-12-08 |website=Radio Free Europe Romania |language=ro}}</ref>

